{"type":"question","id":8185,"title":"如何评价9月6日晚香港示威者前去沙田凯悦酒店「祝贺」新婚警察的行为？","uid":3685,"topics":[2158,2143,17],"contents":"起因是有网友在连登论坛上贴出帖子，爆出9月6日晚有警察将在沙田凯悦酒店摆酒席庆新婚。原贴内含大量个人信息及「男方被戴绿帽」等未经查实的指控，观者自酌。<br>\n<a href=\"https://amp.lihkg.com/thread/1545408/page/1?__twitter_impression=true\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">原贴</a><br>\n随后6日当晚就有大量黑衣示威者前去「祝贺」新婚警官。<br>\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1546419/page/1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">连登论坛直播贴</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/singsingarsing/status/1169936344014979072?s=19\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">现场视频</a><br>\n「阿吴sir，戴绿帽了」<br>\n<br>\n網傳晚上有警員在沙田凱悅酒店擺酒結婚，有小量市民在酒店附近聚集，在門外撤溪錢、用鐳射筆照射進場的賓客等，附近一帶高速公路有大量警察聚集候命。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDx4uxdVAAAJR4L?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDx4uxdVAAAJR4L?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDx4uxdVAAAJR4L?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\nHKUSU 香港大學學生會校園電視：【沙田即時】有人於接近凱悅酒店的中大鄭家純樓向今晚結婚的警察送上祝福。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDxkh2uUEAIMuKx?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDxkh2uUEAIMuKx?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDxkh2uUEAIMuKx?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-09-07","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}